item.title: 【Introductions & Farewells】Hello from Zaida :)
item.description:
Hello dear ShareMania Community,

I’m Zaida, 27 years old and from Germany.

I’m proud to be member and glad I found my way to you.

My Music Taste is related to Epic/Trailer Music.
The Company’s who releases Music for Movie Trailers and to the industry.
(audiomachine, Two Steps From Hell, immediate Music etc.)

I’m the only one here to likes that kind of music? Or are here others too with the same interests?
Sadly I checked the search and here isn’t any trailer music yet.
I think, we can change that ;)

I’m also interested into/looking for industry releases, which aren’t available yet to the Public like Apple Music, Spotify etc. These company’s make them only available to the Movie Industry.
Maybe this great community can help to fill my needs.

Anyways that’s all for now.

Looking forward to share with you ;)

Wish you a great Friday

Kindly Regards
Zaida
